ith known constraints from holography, a weakly back-reacting bulk also forces\nthese skewed tensor network models to the \"large $N$ limit\" where they are\nbuilt by concatenating a large $N$ number of copies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Oct 2020 18:39:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 May 2021 15:33:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-02"}
