ain, is rigorously studied and\nquantified. Moreover, multi-cavern simulations are conducted to investigate the\ninfluence of a cavern on the adjacent caverns.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Oct 2020 18:37:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 31 Oct 2021 23:34:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-02"}
